    "MissionGiver": "Citizens for Prosperity",
    "Title": "Distribute Supplies Across ~mission(Destination)",
    "Description": "Hey,\n\nWe need someone to make a couple runs if you\u2019re interested. Some important supplies need to be distributed across ~mission(Location). Here are the details. \n\nEverything needs to be picked up from <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> then distributed to the following spots: \n\nPackage <EM4>#~mission(Item1|SerialNumber)</EM4> to <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>.\nPackage <EM4>#~mission(Item4|SerialNumber)</EM4> to <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>.\nPackage <EM4>#~mission(Item5|SerialNumber)</EM4> to <EM4>~mission(Destination1|Address)</EM4>.\nPackage <EM4>#~mission(Item2|SerialNumber)</EM4> to <EM4>~mission(Destination1|Address)</EM4>.\nPackage <EM4>#~mission(Item3|SerialNumber)</EM4> to <EM4>~mission(Destination2|Address)</EM4>.\n\nShouldn\u2019t be too difficult. Plus, it\u2019ll give you the chance to familiarize yourself with the outpost and see all the good work the CFP is doing.\n\nAlso, to make your life easier, I'd make sure you have a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> with you. \n\nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
